CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: rYojbaba's primary mission is to improve and restore physical and mental health diminished by work related stress through its consulting and health services. Its consulting services provide labor and corporate consulting services to foster constructive employment relationships between companies and their employees. More specifically, it provides consulting services to labor unions as well as to companies wishing to build constructive relationships with labor unions. Health services are provided through 27 osteopathic clinics and two osteopathic beauty salons to alleviate physical ailments primarily created by work related stress.
